Buidling customize libusb and binary against to android NDK.
===========================================================

1) setup NDK_PATH
   export NDK_PATH=/file/to/ndk
2) build script
   1.  build libusb standalone
       ./build.sh libusb
   2.  build binary standalone
       ./build.sh sources
   3.  build all
       ./build.sh all
   4.  cleanup
       ./build.sh clean
   5. pack all and upload
       ./build.sh pack


